ED_Title: Appointment of the Under-Secretary-General for Internal Oversight Services
ED_DecisionText: At its 85th plenary meeting, on 28 May 2019, the General Assembly took note of the Secretary-General’s proposed action as contained in his note.
ED_Disclaimer: (See A/73/876; A/73/PV.85) The final version of this decision will be contained in document A/73/49 (Vol. III), after editorial review.
